    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Swing Into Action!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Swingers, you navigate the beautiful—and sometimes dangerous—rainforest, swinging by your tongue between branches combined with well-timed jumps between to maintain your momentum. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Swing side to side and manipulate your tongue length to optimize your speed and trajectory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >These unique swinging mechanics, create a satisfying swinging experience with a higher skill-cap than your average platformer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133790/extras/831816f3a68525a67e74f57f8a41d9bf.poster.avif?t=1741990226\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133790/extras/831816f3a68525a67e74f57f8a41d9bf.webm?t=1741990226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133790/extras/831816f3a68525a67e74f57f8a41d9bf.mp4?t=1741990226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Explore!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover 8 secret chameleons hidden throughout the rainforest. Giving one a lick will unlock it's skin for you to play as.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >11 hats can be unlocked by completing Steam Achievements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133790/extras/915e10f622ea2b9529fb591451b81fb8.poster.avif?t=1741990226\" width=390 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133790/extras/915e10f622ea2b9529fb591451b81fb8.webm?t=1741990226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Calling All Speedrunners!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Swingers has a built-in splits to track your current and best times for different segments so you can focus on optimizing your route and mechanics and see your time savings. Compare your personal bests to your friends', favorite streamers', or the global leaderboards!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Will you finish first—if at all?</strong></p>",
